item.title: About me
item.description: Hi, I’m Varun AK! I’m currently a student of Computer Science and Engineering, and I’m passionate about all things related to technology. From a young age, I’ve always been fascinated by how computers work and how they can be used to solve complex problems. During my studies, I’ve gained valuable experience in programming, web development, and database management. I’m always eager to learn new technologies and explore different areas within the field.
